sentence: Wednesday's session closes with the NASDAQ Composite Index reaching a historical high.
The index closed at 5,295.18 up 53.83 for the day.
The index first reached the 5000 mark on 09/07/2016 The total shares traded for the NASDAQ was over 1.94 billion.
Advancers stocks led declining by 2.64 to 1 ratio.
There were 2103 advancers and 796 decliners for the day.
On the NASDAQ Stock Exchange 60 stocks reached a 52 week high and 17 reaching lows.
The most active, advancers, decliners, unusual volume and most active by dollar volume can be monitored intraday on the Most Active Stocks page.
The NASDAQ 100 index closed up 1.01% for the day; a total of 48.53 points.
Netflix, Inc. ( NFLX ) had the largest percent change down (-3.43%) while Adobe Systems Incorporated ( ADBE ) had the largest percent change gain rising 7.12%.
The Dow Jones index closed up .9% for the day; a total of 163.74 points.
Procter & Gamble Company (The) ( PG ) had the largest percent change down (-.88%) while Boeing Company (The) ( BA ) had the largest percent change gain rising 2.17%.
